profile: Spitz Enterprize is committed to quality workmanship and total customer satisfaction. We are a full Handyman service, specializing in kitchens, bathrooms, basements, flooring, drywall, painting and general interior/exterior repairs around the home. Our trades are skilled professionals, detailed and take pride of the end result. Projects are completed on time and within budget. We do the job right the first time.
